DPRFASCN  DIM       2      2        17    Scan Flag
.                                              0 = Debtor File
.                                              1 = PMI
.
PRFAACTN  DIM       3      3        19    Future Action Code
PRFACOMM  DIM       60     60       22    Comments
PRFAMPRA  DIM       6      6        82    Medical Practice
PRFADTCP  DIM       8      8        88    Date Action Completed (CCYYMMDD)
PRFACDAT  DIM       8      8        96    Date Record Created (CCYYMMDD)
PRFACTIM  DIM       8      8        104   Time Record Created (HH:MM:SS)
PRFACUID  DIM       10     10       112   WEB User ID Created (websecaf)
PRFAUDAT  DIM       8      8        122   Date Record Updated (CCYYMMDD)
PRFAUTIM  DIM       8      8        130   Time Record Updated (HH:MM:SS)
